sellerCard.description: I'm Ahmad, a Webflow Professional Partner, Global Leader, and Template Designer with 7 years of experience. I specialise in Webflow design, development, and SEO, ensuring your website is optimized for search engines and delivers a seamless user experience. Partner with me to create a standout website and enjoy free support for 3 months.

description.content:
Hello there,

Want to convey your brand values and a consistent message for your audience? I have helped businesses of all sizes & startups by digging deep into their core values and helping them achieve their goals by making profitable websites.


As a experienced webflow developer, I will develop a unique website that follows google standards, ensuring a speed optimized and responsive site that looks amazing on each device.


Key Features:

  • Pixel perfect Webflow website
  • Webflow Landing Page
  • Functional Webflow CMS
  • Ecommerce Functionality
  • Webflow animations & Interactions
  • Custom CSS/HTML/Javascript
  • On-Page SEO
  • Integrating 3rd party plugins, API's and libraries
  • Multi-language support
  • Domain Integration & Hosting Setup
  • Complete training that how to use webflow editor
  • 1 Year support for small changes/maintaining site


What will Provide me:

  • The design file in PSD, FIGMA, XD, SKETCH, INVISION, ZEPLIN, etc.
  • Any other content or assets


Everything mentioned above in key features is not included fully in packages. This gig offers only developing services.


Contact me now if you have any questions to begin your website today!

slide.name: develop webflow website design and convert figma to webflow

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide design services as well?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Certainly, however, this gig primarily focuses on development services. For comprehensive design solutions, please reach out to me directly to discuss a custom package. Thank you very much

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You will need to provide the design files (Figma, Adobe XD, PSD, Sketch, etc.), logos, photos, text, fonts, and any other relevant files.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you charge on projects?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The price is determined by the design, delivery time, and functionality rather than the number of pages or products. Our packages are designed to give you an estimate of the price range. For large-scale projects, we offer custom solutions tailored to your needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you build a multilingual website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can integrate multilingual functionality by using integrations.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer help or revision after project completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, our services include 3 months of support for minor changes. Please note that free support covers tasks such as updating content, adjusting colors, adding images, or modifying existing elements. However, complete redevelopment or redesigning of the entire website will not be included.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you have a portfolio of your work to share?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I have a list of portfolio websites on Blogspot. Please open the chat board and let us know.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the website be mobile friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, of course. All packages include responsives services

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you need to share login credentials?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, we will develop the website on our team account. After everything is approved by you, we will transfer the website to your Webflow account. We only need access to your account for making changes and maintaining the site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can guide us which webflow plan is suitable for my needs?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, if you're not familiar with Webflow, we'll be happy to assist you.
